&lt;p&gt;This is a fantastic opportunity for a motivated individual to progress in their healthcare management career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Following a restructure of the Medical Director&#39;s Office, a new post has been created: the Medical Professional Standards Manager. This is a vital post that will ensure all aspects of Medical Appraisal and Medical Revalidation run smoothly, including the associated reporting. In addition, the post-holder will have the opportunity to develop a small team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is offered as 0.6 WTE (22.5 hours per week). There is considerably flexibility in how this can be delivered, for example over three, four or five days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jeff Ashby  Business Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email addressJeff.Ashby@ULH.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
